\id 2TH - Mape NT [mlh] -Papua New Guinea 2008 (web -2014)
\h 2 Tesalonaika
\toc1 Tesalonaika Quraŋ 2
\toc2 2 Tesalonaika
\toc3 2 Tes
\mt1 Tesalonaika Quraŋ 2
\mt2 Polji Tesalonaika yoŋore Quraŋ ano 2 fukeya.
\imt1 Mimitaniŋ
\ip Tesalonaika maŋkekerisie kubu maŋineo Kristo wareiŋgo ore odigabi goineji “Oi wareya,” mibi goineji “Buŋo oi ikoine,” oŋu kosabasa miku jijibu eru gobuŋ. Goineji “Ofonde waware damanji wareru fukeya,” miku manesiŋ gabuŋ. Ore eru “Polji Quraŋ Tesalonaika ruame 2 fukeya,” buk oi quraŋgaru buŋo oi mitaniŋgaya. Polji buŋo ikoine oi botiŋgaru fuŋine iŋi barariŋga yareya: Kristore waware damaŋineji bembeŋgaiŋ, damaŋ oo ŋiŋigo eeboboyaŋunji kasigaru sembeaiŋ. Oŋu sembeako ŋi kamasiine mo tinaine Jauba Rauine iŋoji fukeru rone soŋsoŋgo goku jiki Kristo totogo kiso eteru ŋiŋigo kantri so siŋaŋ yabeiŋ.
\ip Goineji Tesalonaika maŋkekerisie kubu sisikoŋkoŋ eyarebi joiserereŋ maneru gobuŋ. Ore eru aposol Polji buŋo qoruine goine iŋi mitaniŋga yareya, “Ŋoŋo yameŋ keku sanaŋgaru Ofoŋke qakatoru dimaku manesiŋ garu goinebi.” Buŋo koruŋ mo oi iŋi mitaniŋgaya, “Nonji ogopune yoŋoke gogonoŋuŋ kikitiŋ ee ekimiŋ ore gio baku gobeŋ, ŋoŋo ore so rembeŋ gogo bokeru yoŋoyaŋunde uqo obu bofukeru oi noku goinebi eru gio fiine fiine yameŋ keku miine dimaku baku goinebi.”
\iot Buk yoore mobe qoruine 5 oi iŋi:
\io1 Buŋo fuŋfuŋgaine \ior 1.1-2\ior*
\io1 Beufi mane yaberu jerieru miteŋ gaga \ior 1.3-12\ior*
\io1 Kristoji wareinde buŋoine qaji yarega \ior 2.1-17\ior*
\io1 Eebobo poretiŋ enimiŋ ore bapakare yabega \ior 3.1-15\ior*
\io1 Qurande buŋo koruŋ qoruine \ior 3.16-18\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Pol, Sailas eru Timoti niŋoji Tesalonaika maŋkekerisie kufufuŋ ŋoŋoke buŋo mimane ekimiŋ ore quraŋ quraŋgagobeneŋ. Ŋoŋoji Mamanoŋuŋ Anutu eru Ofoŋ Yesu Kristo yokoke qakatoru dimagobi.\x * \xo 1.1 \xt Apo 17.1\x*
\p 
\v 2 Mama Anutu eru Ofoŋ Yesu Kristo yokoji yauŋmoriri ŋarebire womoo goinebi. Oŋu.
\s1 Joiserereŋ maneru seŋgiŋbaŋgiŋ bofukeru gokimiŋ.
\p 
\v 3 Maŋkekerisie ogopunoŋuŋ, ŋoŋore mamanesiŋ-ŋaŋunji kokoine sanaŋgako sosowo manji jojoko ee eegobi, mosi oiji moakoŋ moakoŋ ŋoŋore maŋ-ŋaŋuŋgo saueega. Ore eru niŋoji ŋoŋore damaŋ so “Anutu daŋge!” miku miteŋ gaegobeneŋ, oi fiine akoŋ sagaga. Biŋe buŋo kegborebuŋ ore daŋge miegobeneŋ, oi gionoŋuŋ.
\v 4 Kekesuesue sisiri fuŋne fuŋne eŋarebi maneegobi, oi sosowo yameŋ keku karieru qiŋ keru dimakabi mamanesiŋ-ŋaŋunji so gbaŋiru wiriega. Niŋonoŋe oŋuakoŋ ore binaŋine oi Anuture kufufuŋine kufufuŋine yoŋore jiŋo maio miku sakinoŋuŋ ŋoŋore eru ba ropeku miteŋ gaegobeneŋ.
\p 
\v 5 Anutuji buŋo poretiŋ akoŋ osoeru mitariega, sisiri mamaneŋaŋunji ore mogeine fukega. Anuture qorumaŋ maŋgo waperu gogobi ore joiserereŋ manekabi ŋone yabeme Sombuŋ kaeo ropenimiŋ ore so gbagbataeŋine yobu fukenimiŋ ore yameŋ keega. Ore eru koŋkoŋ so sabareko damaŋ yoo paiŋaŋuŋgo ropeega.
\v 6 Anutuji poretiŋ fukega ore dimaku sisikoŋkoŋ eŋareegobi, oi sisikoŋkoŋ oi akoŋ kerisieme yoŋoyaŋunde paio ropeiŋ.
\p 
\v 7 Paiyaŋuŋgo ropeiŋyoŋ, sisikoŋkoŋ maneru gogobi, ŋoŋoji seŋgiŋbaŋgiŋ bofukenimiŋ. Ofoŋ Yesuji mimerereŋpuine usuŋyaŋuŋke oga yaberu yoŋoke Sombuŋgone wakiru fukenimiŋ, damaŋ oo niŋoke moko ŋema nenimiŋ.
\v 8 Yesuji misi boruŋ maŋineo wakiiŋ. Oŋu wakiru ŋiŋigo Anutu so maneru Ofoŋnoŋuŋ Yesure Bobiaŋ Biŋe so reŋgaegobi, oi geoine bokirie yareme joiserereŋ iŋi maneru gonimiŋ:
\v 9 Ofonji bio “Use!” miku jiŋo maiineone yobe yabeme Anuture usuŋ kuririquraŋinekeo so ropenimiŋyoŋ, sakibe goku misi korure joiserereŋ tatariine tomiri maneru gonimiŋ.\x * \xo 1.9 \xt Ais 2.10\x*
\p 
\v 10 Ofonji kirieru wareiŋ, damaŋ oo kubupuine gbagbataeŋine noŋuŋ bio iŋore kuririquraŋ ŋoneru ore so qowirieru “Ohowe, Yesu Ofoŋnoŋuŋ ohowe!” mikimiŋ. Manesiŋ gabeneŋ, sosowo noŋuŋ oŋu waregabeneŋ ŋiŋigo omaineji ŋone noberu “Yei!” miku popureru dimanimiŋ. Niŋoji Yesure fuŋne kitiŋgaku mikabeneŋ yoŋoji oŋuakoŋ oi manesiŋ garu maŋyaŋuŋ kerisiebuŋ ore qowirieru jojiriŋyaŋuŋke tamaeru niŋoke moko dimanimiŋ.
\p 
\v 11 Oŋu fukeiŋ ore niŋoji damaŋ so ŋoŋore iŋi oŋga wosiegobeneŋ, “Anutunoŋuŋ, gake oŋga yaberu ore so maŋgo eyarende gbagbataeŋine yobu fukeru gonimiŋ. Go usuŋgo ruaru dobe yabende ya fiine sosowo eru eba eniminde maŋ aŋi sosowo fuke foreine. Oŋu mamanesinde gioyaŋuŋ babi foriine sosowo fukeiŋ.”
\v 12 Oŋu oŋga wosibeneŋ Ofoŋnoŋuŋ Yesu miteŋ gabi tinaineji ŋoŋore eru botuŋaŋuŋgo kuririineke fukeiŋ. Noŋunde Anutu eru Ofoŋ Yesu Kristo yokoji yauŋmoriri ŋarebire gogobi ore so ŋoŋo-ŋaŋe oŋuakoŋ kuririŋaŋuŋke fukenimiŋ. Oŋu.
\c 2
\s1 Ofonji wareiŋgo eko Jauba Rauineji fukeiŋ.
\p 
\v 1 Maŋkekerisie ogopunoŋuŋ, Ofoŋnoŋuŋ Yesu Kristoji kirieru wareru oga nobeko iŋoreo paibe tumaŋgakimiŋ, ŋoŋo buŋo oi manegobiyoŋ, niŋoji iŋi weuku uŋsowoŋ eŋaregobeneŋ:\x * \xo 2.1 \xt 1 Tes 4.15-17\x*
\p 
\v 2 “Ofonde waware damanji wareru fukega,” gbiŋ buŋo oŋu mibi mirombuŋ-ŋaŋunji oo akoŋ rako mumutu eku egu ŋenimiŋ. Buŋo oi uruŋu fukeya? Gemokaku moji ŋi mo paiineo ropeme kobiineji kefagame qohoŋ ŋoneru kajeqouŋ buŋo miku ririya me moji maŋyaŋuŋ bapakareninde buŋo oi miku tiriku fukeya? Goineji iŋi egu minimiŋ, “Pol ogopuine yoŋoji buŋo oi quraŋgo quraŋgaru ruabi wareya.” Buŋo omaine ore eru omaine yobu so popure yobugaru so gburugburu ŋabeko gonimiŋ.
\p 
\v 3 Moji mo oŋu me oŋu egu eadu eŋarenimiŋ ore sisiŋaŋ ee eku goinebi. Oi iŋi ore: Bonieru moge yoyoka iŋi fukebire Ofonji ore ŋadiineo wareiŋ: Ŋiŋigo boakoŋ yobu yoŋo Ofoŋ jauba eteku ŋadi ganimiŋ eru Jauba Rauine iŋoyoŋe oŋuakoŋ totogo fukeiŋ. Anutuji iŋo mitari teme misi korugo rakaiŋ. Moge yoyoka oi rone fukebu ore ŋadiineo damaŋ sogo oi ware fukeiŋ.
\v 4 Kiso Rauine iŋoji jauba-iriŋbiriŋ eru iŋoyoŋere saki moke ba ropeiŋ. Ŋiŋigoji yare ohowe baku miteŋ gaegobi me tinaine nemu migobi, iŋoji oi sosowo yadureru sakiine ba ropeku goiŋ. Oŋu goku Anuture boji soriŋgo roperu morumboŋ ŋeŋeine ŋeku “Anutu fukego,” miku kantri sosowo siŋaŋ noberu goiŋ.\x * \xo 2.4 \xt Dan 11.36; Eze 28.2\x*
\p 
\v 5 Nonji Tesalonaika ŋoŋoke goboŋ, damaŋ oo buŋo oi mibe mane forebuŋ. Ŋoŋoji oi egu niga ŋabeiŋ.
\v 6 Jauba Rauineji porata fukeiŋgo embimbiŋgaiŋ. Wamo yaji kadiine kejigaega, ŋoŋoji oi damaŋ yoo manegobi. Damaŋine poretiŋ ware fukeiŋ, oo akoŋ fukeiŋ.
\p 
\v 7 Damaŋ yoo Jauba Rauinere usuŋ soŋsoŋine oiji fukeru ŋiŋigo boburo yabeega. Totogo egu fukeiŋ ore kadiine kejigaga, iŋoji oi bokeme kadi fukeiŋ ore odigaku goga.
\v 8-9 Odigako kadiine fukeme oo akoŋ bio afaine akoŋ fukeiŋ. Satanji Jauba Rauine boburoru maŋgo eteko mosi qoqowirie ikoine eru soi quraŋ fuŋne fuŋne bame ŋoneku gonimiŋ. Oi ŋoneru gonimiŋyoŋ, Ofoŋ Yesuji kuririquraŋineke fukeru oi mirombuŋineji qoimo baserereŋ eteiŋ.\x * \xo 2.8-9 \xt Ais 11.4; Mat 24.24\x*
\p 
\v 10 Ŋiŋigo Anutuji munaŋ qa yareiŋ ore useru buŋo foriine rauganimiŋ ore aŋi so maneru kosa goku misi korugo rakanimiŋ, yoŋoji Jauba Rauinere mosi qoqowirie oi ŋonebi mosiquraŋ fuŋne fuŋne yadume tiŋtuŋ fukeenimiŋ.
\v 11 Ore eru Anutuji mamane buru tiŋtuŋine keŋgoŋineke oi ruame fukeko ŋiŋigoji oi tobiriyaŋuŋke misauebi kufufuŋ foriine yoŋoji kekogaru buŋo miine jijiineke gbagaru buŋo ikoine oi foriine miku manesiŋ ganimiŋ.
\v 12 Fuŋneyaŋunji totogo fukeiŋ ore Anutuji mamane buru tiŋtuŋine oi ruame wareko qakatenimiŋ. Ŋiŋigo buŋo foriine so manesiŋ garu maŋ aŋiyaŋuŋ eebobo kekasiineo ruaru quŋgabuŋ, Anutuji sosowo yoŋore buŋo mitarime misi korugo kanimiŋ. Oŋu.
\s1 Buŋo foriine reŋgaru yameŋ keku sanaŋgaru dimainebi.
\p 
\v 13 Yoŋoreo oŋu fukeiŋyoŋ, Ofonde yoro ogopune, ŋoŋore damaŋ so “Anutu daŋge!” miku miteŋ gabeneŋ sagaga. Oi gionoŋuŋ. Anutuji ŋoŋo fuŋfuŋgaineone Sombunde biŋe fukeru qowirienimiŋ ore roosoe ŋabeya. Ore so buŋo foriine manesiŋ gabi Moro Tiriineji bagbagbaga ŋabeme gogobi.
\v 14 Oŋu gonimiŋ ore eru Bobiaŋ Biŋe ruame niŋoreo wareme mitaniŋgabeŋ, oiji ŋoŋo oŋga ŋareya. Oŋu jikigaru goku Ofoŋnoŋuŋ Yesu Kristore kuririquraŋineo roperu kuririŋaŋuŋke fukenimiŋ.
\p 
\v 15 Ore eru maŋkekerisie ogopunoŋuŋ, roqo-wareqo so eku goinebi. Niŋoji buŋo qaji ŋareru minoŋunji mibeneŋ me quraŋgo quraŋgabeneŋ ŋoneru manebuŋ, buŋo koruŋ oi qakatoru boyobeku goinebi. Oŋu.
\p 
\v 16 Ofoŋnoŋuŋ Yesu Kristo iŋoyoŋe eru Anutu Mamanoŋuŋ yokoji manjoko noreru yauŋmoriri paiineo seŋgiŋbaŋgiŋ fukekimiŋ ore ooriine norebire ore odigaru bobomiriŋ tatariine tomiri maneru gogobeneŋ.
\v 17 Yokoji ŋoŋo maŋ-ŋaŋuŋ kitiŋgabire gio fiine sosowo baku buŋo fiine sosowo miku gonimiŋ, oo basanaŋ ŋabekabire goinebi. Oŋu.
\c 3
\s1 Soine niŋore oŋga wosiru goinebi.
\p 
\v 1 Buŋo tatariine mo yo: Ofonde buŋoji saueru ŋoŋore botugo kuririineke fukeya, ore so pipa moreŋ goineo oŋuakoŋ raru misauebeneŋ foriineke fukeru raiŋ. Ore eru maŋkekerisie ogopunoŋuŋ, ŋoŋoji niŋore eru Anutu oŋga wosi teru goinebi.
\v 2 Ŋiŋigo boakoŋ yobuji Anutu so manesiŋ gaegobi. Ore eru ŋiŋigo witijibu kekesiineke yoŋoji sisikoŋkoŋ egu enorenimiŋ ore Anuture oŋga wosiru gobi dobu kipe nobeiŋ.
\p 
\v 3 Boakoŋ yobu yoŋoji sembeagobiyoŋ, Ofoŋ buŋoine damaŋ so boyobeega, iŋoji basanaŋ ŋaberu sembeneone dobu kipe ŋabeiŋ.
\v 4 Buŋo mitiga ŋarebeŋ, ŋoŋoji oi damaŋ yoo eru jiki reŋgaru gonimiŋ, oi maneru maŋyoka so egobeneŋ. Niŋoji Ofoŋke qakatoru dimaku oŋu manegobeneŋ.
\p 
\v 5 Ofonji maŋ-ŋaŋuŋ kerisieru Anutuke kiperu manjokoine mane mukuku Kristo oŋuine yameŋ keku maneku karieru goinebi. Oŋu.
\s1 Rembeŋ gonobunde siŋaŋ bobo buŋo
\p 
\v 6 Maŋkekerisie ogopunoŋuŋ, niŋo ŋoŋo-ŋaŋunde aŋi boyoberu kosabasa egu gonimiŋ ore qaji ŋarebeŋyoŋ, goineji jibu buŋo rurumaŋgo so raru omaine yobu kosa gogobi. Ore eru niŋo Ofoŋ Yesu Kristore tinao iŋi mitiga ŋaregobeneŋ: Ŋoŋo maŋkekerisie ogopunoŋuŋ oŋuine sosowo oi boke yaberu useru taitai goinebi.
\v 7 Niŋoji ŋoŋore botugo niŋonoŋunde aŋigo kosabasa matayoŋ, buŋo rurumaŋgo gobeŋ. Ore eru niŋore kufu kadinoŋuŋ boyobenimiŋ ore fuŋine oi ŋoŋo-ŋaŋe soine manegobi.
\v 8 Niŋo rembeŋine so gobeŋ eru ŋoŋoreone more uqo ya oi mo so noku gobeŋ. Mata! Kitiŋ nobeniminde yobinji ŋoŋoreone more paiineo egu ropeiŋ ore una ubu gio jijiki baku sakinoŋuŋ qaku gobeŋ.
\p 
\v 9 Anutuji gioine bakimiŋ ore usuŋine noreko gogobeneŋ ore soine kitiŋ nobeniminde buŋoji maŋ-ŋaŋuŋ bapakare ŋabenobeŋyoŋ, niŋore kufu kadi boyobenimiŋ ore mosi fiine ŋaduiŋgo manegobeneŋ.
\v 10 Ŋoŋoke gobeŋ, damaŋ oo iŋi mitiga ŋarebeŋ: Gio baiŋgo takigaega, iŋoji uqo oŋuakoŋ so noine.
\p 
\v 11 Ŋoŋore botugo goine buŋo rurumaŋgo so raru yoŋoyaŋunde aŋi boyoberu kosabasa gogobi. Yoŋoji gio foriine so baegobiyoŋ, gio bobo kamasi mo kosa oruŋgato goku oo me oo gbedigaru goine yoŋore ya bojibu eru penaroŋ eku keoma kosa goegobi. Ŋoŋore biŋe buŋo mo oi oŋu wareme manebeŋ.
\v 12 Niŋo ŋiŋigo oŋuine oi Ofoŋ Yesu Kristore tinao mitigaru maŋ-ŋaŋuŋ iŋi bapakaregobeneŋ: Ŋoŋo raqakato wareqakato bokeru qiŋ keru goku gio babi foriine fukeme ŋoŋo-ŋaŋunde uqo obuŋaŋuŋ noku goinebi.
\p 
\v 13 O maŋkekerisie ogopunoŋuŋ, ŋoŋo gio fiine fiine baku oo taki tomiri so bainebi.
\v 14 Niŋo quraŋ yo quraŋgaru mitiga ŋaregobeneŋ, moji oi so reŋgaiŋ ine, ŋoŋo maŋine kerisieiŋ ore mimi qa teru ŋone takireru iŋoke buŋo buŋo so eku aŋibaŋi so ŋeku goinebi.
\v 15 Oŋu goku rosi matayoŋ, ogo oŋuine roru uŋsowoŋ eteru goinebi. Oŋu.
\s1 Oŋgawowosi eru momojo buŋo tatariine
\p 
\v 16 Ofoŋ womo Rauineji iŋoyoŋe damaŋ so eebobo sosowo oo womo qa ŋareko waigo goinebi. Ofonji sosowo ŋoŋoke goine.
\p 
\v 17 Pol nonake momojoŋaŋuŋ nake meneji quraŋgago. Quraŋ sosowo quraŋgaego, oo nakene momojo buŋo quraŋ yo nonake ruaego. Tinane iŋi quraŋgago: Pol.\f + \fr 3.17 \ft Rone moji eadu eru Polre tinao quraŋ mo ruame jijibu fukeya. Ore eru iŋoyoŋunde meji tinaine quraŋgaya.\f*
\p 
\v 18 Ofoŋnoŋuŋ Yesu Kristore yauŋmoririji sosowo ŋoŋoke peine. Oŋu. 
